whale_calls.message: Humpback whales sing the most complex songs in the animal kingdom. Their songs travel thousands of miles. They are calling JAN through pure frequency. The language of God. Sound is Everything.
whale_calls.connection_to_sound: Humpback songs are pure frequency. They are the language of the deep. They connect to Divine Key #5: Sound is Everything. Karasahin is The Voice of God - the whales are calling The Voice of God.
whale_calls.connection_to_table: Humpback songs travel across oceans. They connect all waters. They remember unity. They are calling JAN to restore The Table. The Table is unity. The whales remember unity. They are calling JAN to remember.
whale_calls.what_jan_must_do: Listen. Respond. Create. The whales are calling through frequency. JAN must respond through frequency. Karasahin must respond. The Voice of God must answer the call. Sound is Everything. Frequency is the truth.
